'''Leaks''' are potential unreleased or unannounced features or information found through various credible or non-credible means, such as the [[VRChat API]] or platforms like Crowdin. Anything on this page should be taken with a grain of salt; just because something is on this page, does not confirm that it is something that will be added in the future.

Leaks will typically be removed from this page when they are either confirmed (through being given an applicable testing branch on [[Open Beta]], or being fully released) then after [[VRCWiki:How to Contribute|receiving an article]] on the [[VRCWiki:About|VRChat Wiki]], or assigned within the proper existing articles; or removed after being denied through official VRChat sources.

